Package client

Class ViewManager

java.lang.Object
client.ViewManager
public class ViewManager
extends java.lang.Object
ViewManager is a Singleton. Class handles all different views and their transitions. ViewManager is Singleton. The instance is initially created in getInstance() with lazy initialization.

The Scenes of the view can be changed with nextScenes() and previousScene(). showMenu() return to the main menu.

Author:
Simon, sarah
